name: readPairOrientation
description: the relative orientation of the reads in a paired-end protocol

name: readPairOrientation
enumValues_description: reads face away from each other

name: readStrandOrigin
description: the strand from which the read originates in a strand-specific protocol
enumValues_description: read 1 (or unpaired read) comes from the forward strand and read 2 (if applicable) comes from the reverse strand; equivalent to Tophat 'fr-secondstrand' type

name: readStrandOrigin
enumValues_description: read 1 (or unpaired read) comes from the reverse strand and read 2 (if applicable) comes from the forward strand; equivalent to Tophat 'fr-firststrand' type
